			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">This is acutally kind of a strange thing. I have gone FD, told my pet to FD, then waited for "enemies forgotten" message. Then I stand just before pet poofs, and chill a moment as pet is FD. But sometimes, even if you wait long enough, when the pet gets up its BAM BAM BAM. So I don't htink you can ever really count on it working. By far your best bet is simply to suspend minion once he is FD, that will definately wipe the aggro.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
