			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">pet fd works on most of the same mechanics as ours.
<br />

<br />
simple pet fd will give a chance to wipe agro.
<br />

<br />
pet fd and having him stand when mob has returned to spawn point gives a very high chance to wipe agro.
<br />

<br />
if you have agro wiped and you tell your pet to stand, and he has agro, it will transfer to you.. they will beat the shit out of your pet and then come after you.
<br />

<br />
i don't think the 2min thing applies to pets. there is definitely no message for the pet. usually by 2mins, the thing has returned to spawn point and agro is clear anyways. test it on a wanderer sometime..
<br />

<br />
but yes, the best bet is to simply suspend minion after agro is clean on you, and your pet is fd, and then unsuspend. 100% agro wipe there.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
